      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/23/us/politics/trump-thune-senate-election-bill.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[白宫发言人表示，特朗普总统的耐心正在耗尽。参议院共和党领袖表示，她应该尝试争取选票。]]></description>
